Class TrialTreeParameterModel

All Implemented Interfaces:
TreeDoubleTraitProvider, TreeTrait<java.lang.Double>, Model, ModelListener, StatisticList, VariableListener, MPISerializable, Identifiable, java.io.Serializable
public class TrialTreeParameterModel
extends TreeParameterModel

This class maintains a parameter of length equal to the number of nodes in the tree. It can optionally include the root node. If the root node is not included then this class will track tree changes that change the root node number and swap the parameter values so that the parameter values stay with their node when changes to the tree topology occur.

Author:
Alexei Drummond, Marc A. Suchard
